VTH_N.R.1 { @ Overlap of P+ ACTIVE, VTH_P, VTL_N, VTL_P, VTUL_N, VTUL_P, UHVT_N, UHVT_P, EHVT_N, EHVT_P, NT_N, or OD2 is not allowed   
  VTHN AND OD2
