// 'IND.S.7' is checked by IND.S.7:M1
IND.S.7:M1 { @ M1, DM1, and DM1_O /Mx, DMx, and DMx_O /My, DMy, and DMy_O space in (INDDMY SIZING 16 um) [at least one metal line width > 1.5 um (W1) and the parallel run length > 1.5 um (L1)] >= 0.5 
  A = (M1x WITH WIDTH > IND_S_7_W) AND IND_EXD  
  X = EXT A M1x < IND_S_7 OPPOSITE REGION MEASURE ALL
