BDTCD.R.1:M1 { @ TCDDMY_FDM1/ TCDDMY_FM1/ TCDDMY_M1 should contain M1 and DM1EXCL layers. TCDDMY_FDM1/ TCDDMY_FMx/ TCDDMY_Mx should contain Mx and DMxEXCL layers   
  TCDDMY_FM1 OUTSIDE M1
  TCDDMY_FM1 OUTSIDE DM1EXCL
  TCDDMY_M1 OUTSIDE M1
  TCDDMY_M1 OUTSIDE DM1EXCL
  TCDDMY_FDM1 OUTSIDE M1
  TCDDMY_FDM1 OUTSIDE DM1EXCL
}
