BDTCD.R.1:M7 { @ TCDDMY_FDM1/ TCDDMY_FM1/ TCDDMY_M1 should contain M1 and DM1EXCL layers. TCDDMY_FDM1/ TCDDMY_FMx/ TCDDMY_Mx should contain Mx and DMxEXCL layers   
