EFP.VIA2.S.1 { @ VIMB (Via Induce Metal Bridge) rule type-1: "Confined VIAx" space to neighboring VIAx [INTERACT the same Mx and Mx+1 as "Confined VIAx" at the same time] Definition of "Confined VIAx": VIAx enclosure [0 um at one side and < 0.04 um (E1) at adjacent side] by Mx+1 [the edge with 0 um VIAx enclosure space to neighboring Mx+1 < 0.065 um (D1)] >= 0.08 
  COPY EFP_VIA2_S_1 
}
// EFP.VIAx.S.1 is checked by EFP.VIA2.S.1
EFP.VIA2.S.2 { @ VIMB (Via Induce Metal Bridge) rule type-2: "Confined VIAx" space to neighboring VIAx [NOT INTERACT the same Mx and Mx+1 as "Confined VIAx" at the same time] Definition of "Confined VIAx": VIAx enclosure [0 um at one side and < 0.04 um (E1) at adjacent side] by Mx+1 [the edge with 0 um VIAx enclosure space to neighboring Mx+1 < 0.065 um (D1)] >= 0.08 
  COPY EFP_VIA2_S_2 
}
// EFP.VIAx.S.2 is checked by EFP.VIA2.S.2
EFP.VIA2.S.3 { @ VIMB (Via Induce Metal Bridge) rule type-3: "Confined VIAx" space to VIAx [parallel run length > -0.04 um, INTERACT the same Mx and Mx+1 as "Confined VIAx" at the same time] Definition of "Confined VIAx": VIAx enclosure [0 um at one side and < 0.04 um (E1) at adjacent side] by Mx+1 [the edge with 0 um VIAx enclosure space to Mx+1 < 0.065 um (D1)] >= 0.09 
  COPY EFP_VIA2_S_3 
}
// EFP.VIAx.S.3 is checked by EFP.VIA2.S.3
EFP.VIA2.S.4 { @ VIMB (Via Induce Metal Bridge) rule type-4: "Confined VIAx" space to VIAx [parallel run length > -0.04 um, NOT INTERACT the same Mx and Mx+1 as "Confined VIAx" at the same time] Definition of "Confined VIAx": VIAx enclosure [0 um at one side and < 0.04 um (E1) at adjacent side] by Mx+1 [the edge with 0 um VIAx enclosure space to Mx+1 < 0.065 um (D1)] >= 0.09 
  COPY EFP_VIA2_S_4
}
// EFP.VIAx.S.4 is checked by EFP.VIA2.S.4
EFP.VIA2.S.5 { @ VIMB (Via Induce Metal Bridge) rule type-5: "Confined VIAx" space to neighboring rectangular VIAx [INTERACT the same Mx and Mx+1 as "Confined VIAx" at the same time] Definition of "Confined VIAx": VIAx enclosure [0 um at one side and < 0.04 um (E1) at adjacent side] by Mx+1 [the edge with 0 um VIAx enclosure space to neighboring Mx+1 < 0.065 um (D1)] >= 0.085 
  COPY EFP_VIA2_S_5 
