RR:RE:M5.S.5 { @ Recommended space [at least one metal line width > 0.63 um] >= 0.15 
  ((EXT M5_23 M5 < M5_S_5_R OPPOSITE REGION MEASURE ALL) NOT M5) INTERACT M5S5_M5
}
