RR:RE:M7.DN.6 { @ Recommend metal Density >= ^M7_DN_6_R for IP level. Item(A) to Item(C) are recommended.
@ (A) For IP level, recommend metal density [checking window ^M7_DN_6_W_A_R um x ^M7_DN_6_W_A_R um, stepping ^M7_DN_6_S_A_R um] >= ^M7_DN_6_R
@ (B) For IP level, recommend maximum area of merged low density windows [checking window ^M7_DN_6_W_BC_R um x ^M7_DN_6_W_BC_R um, stepping ^M7_DN_6_S_BC_R um, density < ^M7_DN_6_R] <= ^M7_DN_6_A_B_R um2. Merged low density windows width <= ^M7_DN_6_U_R um is excepted.
@ (C) For IP level, recommend maximum area of merged low density windows [checking window ^M7_DN_6_W_BC_R um x ^M7_DN_6_W_BC_R um, stepping ^M7_DN_6_S_BC_R um, density < ^M7_DN_6_R] <= ^M7_DN_6_A_C_R um2
