//*************************************************************************************
//* CALIBRE DRC COMMAND FILE - CLN22ULL_028_PATCH.09a 10/29/2021
//* FOR TSMC 22 NM CMOS LOGIC ULTRA LOW POWER DESIGN RULES (PATCH FOR SUHVT) (CLN22ULL/CRN22ULL)
//* DRC COMMAND FILE DOCUMENT: T-N22-CL-DR-028-C1 VER 0.9a
//* DESIGN RULE DOCUMENT:      T-N22-CL-DR-028    VER 0.9
